  "description": "APPLICATION FOR A LAWFUL DEVELOPMENT CERTIFICATE IN RESPECT OF THE PROPOSED ERECTION OF A REAR ROOF EXTENSION WITH INSTALLATION OF ROOFLIGHTS TO THE FRONT SLOPE.",
  "decision_conditions": [
    "Reason : 1 - The proposed rooflight positioned on the flat roof of the proposed rear roof extension would project 0.11m above the highest part of the existing roof contrary to Schedule 2, Part 1, Class B, B.1, (b) which notes development is not permitted where any part of the dwellinghouse would, as a result of the works, exceed the height of the highest part of the existing roof. ",
    "Reason : 2 - The edge of the roof extension would be set in set in 0.12m from the outside edge of the eaves contrary to Schedule 2, Part 1, Class B, B.2, (b) (i) (bb) which states \"the edge of the enlargement closest to the eaves of the original roof shall, so far as practicable, be not less than 0.2 metres from the eaves, measured along the roof slope from the outside edge of the eaves\""
  ],
